Package: GeoStratR
Title: Simple Spatial Stratification of Rasters
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Derek",
           family = "Corcoran",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "derek.corcoran@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0248-6230"))
Description: This software uses either the Calinski-Harabasz criterion or the simple structure index criterion to stratify a raster stack. 
            It also generates different sampling designs for that stratification.
